de.topicmapslab.tmql4j.components.processor.results
Interface IResultSet<T extends IResult>

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
CTMResult, OntopiaResultSet, ResultSet, SimpleResultSet, WrappedOntopiaResultSet, XMLResult
public interface IResultSet<T extends IResult>
extends java.lang.Iterable<T>

Interface definition of a sequence of tuples as a result of querying process. The result set represents a 2-dimension container containing a number of IResults.

Author:
Sven Krosse
